data.description: Welcome to the popular Walden on Lake Houston Subdivision! This 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home is priced to sell. As you enter the home you will see the formal dining room that leads into the living room open to the updated kitchen and breakfast room. Laundry room and half bath are located on the first floor. Upstairs you will find the large primary bedroom with a spacious bathroom and closet! Conveniently located with access to multiple restaurants and shopping. Zoned to Humble ISD schools. Schedule your showing today!
